{"tid":2136817,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（呼籲葛博士跟進）廣州黃花岡七十二烈士公墓存有自由女神像","createTime":"2020-08-02T12:07:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-02T13:54:04.000Z","uid":98659,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ee8e50162fa56fa177f6bf76c56cdee892156e75","tid":2136817,"uid":98659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T12:07:49.000Z","msg":"《 廣州黃花岡七十二烈士公墓紀功坊現「#自由女神像」&mdash; #葛珮帆 會否促拆下？》<br />\n<br />\n辛亥年三月廿九，革命黨起義於廣州，事未成，被滿清發覺。當時殉難者不知其數，後檢殮屍身只有七十二人，遂葬於黃花岡。革命成功後，由國人及政府出資建立偉大之公墓。烈士墓落成之初，紀功坊上曾仿照美國及法國設有象徵共和理想的「自由女神像」，由美洲華僑黨員贈送，神像約有兩米多高，頭戴七束光芒冠冕，左手挾着《 中華民國臨時約法 》，右手舉石槌，正對前方墓塘碑亭頂部之自由鐘，警醒革命者尚未成功，仍需努力。當時在神像腳下，左右各蹲伏着一隻石雕雄鷹，亟待向藍天飛翔。<br />\n<br />\n懇請支持秋海棠民國史地 Patreon<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/GlimpsesOfModernChina\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2FGlimpsesOfModernChina&d=aFheyUS8Hi5o9a%2F4VMBAnZvkp%2FM1ZBOvf84g0fLsyFs%3D&h=baf9dfc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/GlimpsesOfModernChina</a><br />\n<br />\n（資料來源：《 中國大觀圖畫年鑒 &mdash; 民國十九年（1930）年鑒 》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kF3aA4N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkF3aA4N.jpg&h=476ccef9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AbFPRC8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAbFPRC8.jpg&h=4c912301&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ef65685cf5d0a93a0ee80f17a7c1af3c467fd8e2","tid":2136817,"uid":282637,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T12:14:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-ICz5lDA290\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-ICz5lDA290&d=aFheyUS8Hi5o9a%2F4VMBAnZvkp%2FM1ZBOvf84g0fLsyFs%3D&h=a3430a7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-ICz5lDA290</a>"},{"pid":"dcc632700533aeb6aff7fa99d3616712785969e7","tid":2136817,"uid":286966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T12:18:09.000